{
  "texts": [
    "These results provide compelling evidence that while Copilot enhances both capability innovation (through function-adding commits) and iterative innovation (through non-functionadding commits), its impact is substantially greater on iterative innovation.",
    "The effect on non-functionadding commits is approximately 7.5 times larger than the effect on function-adding commits in absolute terms (6.016 vs. 0.800), and 1.5 times larger in percentage terms (39.1% vs. 26.5%).",
